Package edu.iit.sat.itmd4515.bpasham.web

Class PlaceOrderController

java.lang.Object
edu.iit.sat.itmd4515.bpasham.web.PlaceOrderController
@Named @RequestScoped public class PlaceOrderController extends Object
Place order controller to place orders by customers, and delete them. Displays the pages to view order details, and order form page.
